des:
Tune into The Family – Central Wisconsin for hope, strength & encouragement. Listen to artists like Lauren Daigle, Crowder, Chris Tomlin, We The Kingdom, Casting Crowns & Toby Mac. Enjoy encouraging music and uplifting programming. Hang out with show hosts who feel like best friends! 
 
The Family Radio Network is a non-profit Christian radio station that shares the hope of Jesus. To listen to The Family-Central Wisconsin you must enable the skill. Once you’ve enabled the skill, you can say “Alexa, open The Family Central Wisconsin” to start listening. Thanks for tuning in!
